    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-80f1-ace1-ca0eeaf784bf",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that clickstream maps pretty well to the self-reported measures. Also, incorporating these in a predictive model improved the model’s ability to detect student performance over self-reports alone. \n",
